songs.title: Binky Boy
songs.lyrics:
22 years old
Lives with mommy
Billy McDonald's
Afraid to watch TV

Billy boy
Afraid to go outside
Binky has taken
Billy's mind

I'm a big boy
But I can't kick this toy
Binky
I'm a binky
Binky boy

Silicone high
Takes away constant paranoia
Binky
I'm a binky
Binky boy

Toxic trash
Spilt into the town
Chemical waste
Poisoning all around

Billy drank
Straight from mommy's teet
Mommy says
Now I'm too old for it
